 problem rocket hp
     p(bar) = 1
     o/f = 0
 reac
     fuel = Jet-A(L) t(K) = 298.000
     ox = Air t(K) = 1500.000
 outp trans
 end

 OPTIONS: TP=F  HP=T  SP=F  TV=F  UV=F  SV=F  DETN=F  SHOCK=F  REFL=F  INCD=F
 RKT=T  FROZ=F  EQL=F  IONS=F  SIUNIT=T  DEBUGF=F  SHKDBG=F  DETDBG=F  TRNSPT=T

 TRACE= 0.00E+00  S/R= 0.000000E+00  H/R= 0.000000E+00  U/R= 0.000000E+00

 Pc,BAR =     1.000000

 Pc/P =

 SUBSONIC AREA RATIOS =

 SUPERSONIC AREA RATIOS =

 NFZ=  1  Mdot/Ac= 0.000000E+00  Ac/At= 0.000000E+00

 WARNING!!  AMOUNT MISSING FOR REACTANT  1.
 PROGRAM SETS WEIGHT PERCENT = 100. (REACT)

 WARNING!!  AMOUNT MISSING FOR REACTANT  2.
 PROGRAM SETS WEIGHT PERCENT = 100. (REACT)

    REACTANT          WT.FRAC   (ENERGY/R),K   TEMP,K  DENSITY
        EXPLODED FORMULA
 F: Jet-A(L)         1.000000  -0.364971E+05   298.00  0.0000
          C 12.00000  H 23.00000
 O: Air              1.000000   0.464531E+04  1500.00  0.0000
          N  1.56168  O  0.41959  AR 0.00937  C  0.00032

OXIDANT NOT PERMITTED WHEN SPECIFYING 100% FUEL(main)



